## Styling Approach

### CSS-in-JS with styled-jsx

The component uses Next.js's built-in `styled-jsx` for scoped styles. This ensures:
- No style conflicts with other components
- Unique filter IDs per instance
- Full CSS feature support
- Server-side rendering compatibility

### Color System

Uses OKLCH color space for smooth color transformations:

```css
--banner-light-color: oklch(from var(--banner-color) l c h);
--banner-gradient: oklch(from var(--banner-color) 0.3 calc(c / 2) h / 0.3);
```

This creates consistent, perceptually-uniform color variations.

